{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875106731,"sessionID":"ses_2859954bcffewV0OdP2X4fAZVs","part":{"id":"prt_d7a672ca5001YrNmMW4d1ea2zS","messageID":"msg_d7a6711a2001Ts1dAj7dGmAuz7","sessionID":"ses_2859954bcffewV0OdP2X4fAZVs","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_8b01abd079394aa18e797374","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n\n**Module:** docker  \n**Language:** Dockerfile  \n**Size:** S  \n**Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Directory & Base Dockerfile\n\n- [ ] **T001** Create `docker/` directory at project root\n- [ ] **T002** Create `docker/base.Dockerfile` with Go build environment\n  - Base image: `golang:1.24-alpine`\n  - Include go mod download\n  - Build stage named: `builder`\n- [ ] **T003** Add build arguments to base.Dockerfile (GO_VERSION, BUILDER_IMAGE, RUNTIME_IMAGE, BINARY_VERSION)\n- [ ] **T004** Verify `docker build -f docker/base.Dockerfile --target builder -t agentcube-builder:test .` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Router Dockerfile\n\n- [ ] **T010** Create `docker/Dockerfile.router` with multi-stage build\n- [ ] **T011** Builder stage copies source and builds router binary from `cmd/router/main.go`\n- [ ] **T012** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n- [ ] **T013** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n- [ ] **T014** Copy binary from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/router`\n- [ ] **T015** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n- [ ] **T016** Configure ENTRYPOINT for router binary\n- [ ] **T017** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Workload Manager Dockerfile\n\n- [ ] **T020** Create `docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager` with multi-stage build\n- [ ] **T021** Builder stage builds workload-manager binary from `cmd/workload-manager/main.go`\n- [ ] **T022** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n- [ ] **T023** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n- [ ] **T024** Copy binary from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/workload-manager`\n- [ ] **T025** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n- [ ] **T026** Configure ENTRYPOINT for workload-manager binary\n- [ ] **T027** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager -t agentcube-workload-manager:test .` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Agentd Dockerfile\n\n- [ ] **T030** Create `docker/Dockerfile.agentd` with multi-stage build\n- [ ] **T031** Builder stage builds agentd binary from `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n- [ ] **T032** Builder stage builds picod binary from `cmd/picod/main.go`\n- [ ] **T033** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n- [ ] **T034** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n- [ ] **T035** Copy both binaries from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/`\n- [ ] **T036** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n- [ ] **T037** Configure ENTRYPOINT for agentd binary (supports picod as argument)\n- [ ] **T038** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.agentd -t agentcube-agentd:test .` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Binary Execution Verification\n\n- [ ] **T040** Test router binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:test --help` exits 0\n- [ ] **T041** Test workload-manager binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-workload-manager:test --help` exits 0\n- [ ] **T042** Test agentd binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:test --help` exits 0\n- [ ] **T043** Test picod binary: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:test picod --help` exits 0\n- [ ] **T044** Test router version: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:test version` exits 0\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Security Verification\n\n- [ ] **T050** Verify router runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-router:id` shows uid=1000\n- [ ] **T051** Verify workload-manager runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-workload-manager:id` shows uid=1000\n- [ ] **T052** Verify agentd runs as non-root: `docker run --rm agentcube-agentd:id` shows uid=1000\n- [ ] **T053** Verify no source code in router: `docker run --rm agentcube-router ls /build` returns error\n- [ ] **T054** Verify no go.mod in router: `docker run --rm agentcube-router cat go.mod` returns error\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Image Size Verification\n\n- [ ] **T060** Check router image size: `docker images agentcube-router --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 50MB\n- [ ] **T061** Check workload-manager image size: `docker images agentcube-workload-manager --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 50MB\n- [ ] **T062** Check agentd image size: `docker images agentcube-agentd --format \"{{.Size}}\"` < 60MB\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Makefile Integration (Optional)\n\n- [ ] **T070** Add docker-build-router target to Makefile\n- [ ] **T071** Add docker-build-workload-manager target to Makefile\n- [ ] **T072** Add docker-build-agentd target to Makefile\n- [ ] **T073** Add docker-build (all) target to Makefile\n- [ ] **T074** Verify `make docker-build-router` succeeds\n\n---\n\n## Phase 9: Cache Reuse Verification\n\n- [ ] **T080** Run first build (cold): `time docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .`\n- [ ] **T081** Run second build (no changes): `time docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:test .`\n- [ ] **T082** Verify second build completes in < 30 seconds (cache reused)\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n```\nT001 → T002 → T003 → T004\nT010-T017 (Router - depends on T002-T004)\nT020-T027 (Workload Manager - depends on T002-T004)\nT030-T038 (Agentd - depends on T002-T004)\nT040-T044 (Binary tests - depends on T017, T027, T038)\nT050-T054 (Security tests - depends on T040-T044)\nT060-T062 (Size tests - depends on T040-T044)\nT070-T074 (Makefile - can parallel after T040-T044)\nT080-T082 (Cache tests - depends on T017)\n```\n\n**Parallel:** Phase 2, 3, 4 (Router, Workload Manager, Agentd Dockerfiles) can be done in parallel after Phase 1\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `docker/base.Dockerfile` exists with Go builder stage\n- [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.router` builds successfully, image < 50MB\n- [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager` builds successfully, image < 50MB\n- [ ] `docker/Dockerfile.agentd` builds successfully, image < 60MB\n- [ ] All binaries execute correctly inside containers\n- [ ] All containers run as non-root (uid=1000)\n- [ ] No source code present in runtime images\n- [ ] Build cache works correctly (second build < 30s)\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Build all images\ndocker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-router:latest .\ndocker build -f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager -t agentcube-workload-manager:latest .\ndocker build -f docker/Dockerfile.agentd -t agentcube-agentd:latest .\n\n# Binary verification\ndocker run --rm agentcube-router version\ndocker run --rm agentcube-workload-manager --help\ndocker run --rm agentcube-agentd --help\ndocker run --rm agentcube-agentd picod --help\n\n# Security verification\ndocker run --rm agentcube-router id\ndocker run --rm agentcube-router ls /build\n\n# Size verification\ndocker images agentcube-router\ndocker images agentcube-workload-manager\ndocker images agentcube-agentd\n```","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775875106689,"end":1775875106728}}}}
