est .` succeeds\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ## Phase 3: Workload Manager Dockerfile\n36: \n37: - [ ] **T020** Create `docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager` with multi-stage build\n38: - [ ] **T021** Builder stage builds workload-manager binary from `cmd/workload-manager/main.go`\n39: - [ ] **T022** Runtime stage uses `alpine:3.19` as base\n40: - [ ] **T023** Create non-root user `agentcube` (UID 1000)\n41: - [ ] **T024** Copy binary from builder stage to `/usr/local/bin/workload-manager`\n42: - [ ] **T025** Set correct file permissions (chmod +x)\n43: - [ ] **T026** Configure ENTRYPOINT for workload-manager binary\n44: - [ ] **T027** Verify `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.workload-manager -t agentcube-workload-manager:test .` succeeds\n45: \n46: ---\n47: \n48: ## Phase 4: Agentd Dockerfile\n49: \n50: - [ ] **T030** Create `docker/Dockerfile.agentd` with multi-stage build\n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 157. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n\n**Module:** docker  \n**Language:** Dockerfile  \n**Size:** S  \n**Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Directory & Base Dockerfile\n\n- [ ] **T001** Create `docker/` directory at project root\n- [ ] **T002** Create `docker/base.Dockerfile` with Go build environment\n  - Base image: `golang:1.24-alpine`\n  - Include go mod download\n  - Build stage named: `builder`\n- [ ] **T003** Add build arguments to base.Dockerfile (GO_VERSION, BUILDER_IMAGE, RUNTIME_IMAGE, BINARY_VERSION)\n- [ ] **T004** Verify `docker build -f docker/base.Dockerfile --target builder -t agentcube-builder:test .` succeeds\n\n---","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775875110222,"end":1775875110240}}}}
